ACKNOWLEDGMENTS:

This project draws inspiration from autonomous research methodologies and
transformer architectures. The core transformer implementation and optimization
techniques build upon established deep learning practices in the PyTorch
ecosystem.

The cardiovascular dataset used for evaluation is derived from the UCI Machine
Learning Repository Heart Disease dataset.

Third-party libraries used (see pyproject.toml for full list):
- PyTorch: Deep learning framework
- rustbpe: High-performance BPE tokenization
- scikit-learn: Clinical metrics calculation
- pandas, numpy: Data processing
